Package interfaces.services

Interface GenerateReportServiceable

All Superinterfaces:
Exportable
All Known Implementing Classes:
CommitteeGenerateReportService, StaffGenerateReportService
public interface GenerateReportServiceable extends Exportable
The GenerateReportServiceable interface defines the functionality for generating reports related to a camp. It extends the Exportable interface to support exporting the generated reports.

Classes that implement this interface should provide their own implementation for generating reports based on a specified Camp and GenerateType.
